Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Even {\i1}you{\i0} can get nervous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine as long as you know English.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the fudge up, dimwits!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going on a mission overseas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be totally different from Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to concentrate \N'cause I wanna be at peak performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I guess everyone's got \Ntheir own way of coping with stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Some get nervous, some get amped. \NI guess Bakugo is the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Hawks and Tokoyami!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So where are you guys headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got a large area to cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawks' speed will be a valuable asset.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Hawks for you! The fastest man alive! {hold up}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(420,1025)}What? Hawks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\pos(420,1025)}What? {\alpha}Hawks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1280,1025)}What? Hawks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(240,1025)}Hawks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,1025)}Hawks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1288,1025)}Hawks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. Stop, my little chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at the airport. Let's not make a ruckus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no stopping the simps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I getting dragged into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-It's all my fault! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Endeavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(380,350)\shad1\alpha&H30&}Endeavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\shad1\alpha&H50&}Endeavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\shad1\alpha&HA0&}Endeavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\shad1\alpha&HE0&}Endeavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobody approached him at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to board. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Shoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,0)}If it's a joke, I'm not laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to sit next to Midoriya and Bakugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Todoroki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You still think I'm your {\i1}friend{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Change the seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Come on, it's not like it'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can he say something so cute \Nwith such a scary face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I want to sit next to my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Definitely the youngest in the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We are {\i1}not{\i0} friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna enjoy your flight out in the sky\N strapped to the tail of the plane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand me the tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go ignoring me, dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bakugo, can you hold on to this for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you even listening to me, shithead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to Shoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-And {\i0}this{\i1} is supposed to be \NJapan's Number One Hero Agency?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My stress levels have already shot through the sky and into outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, sit in this order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're not grade schoolers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It won't be easy for him to \Ntalk to me since I'm behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh? Shoto will be looking at my back the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Endeavor's sitting right next to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make him spill all the secrets behind his power by the time we land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All's well that ends well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Our flight's about to take-off so we're gonna go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can relax and \Nget ready for World Heroes' Mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(525,1050)}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,1050)}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1460,1050)}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is! Don't run away from us, Hawks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even the fastest man alive got caught twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A faraway land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A world unknown to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we find there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting too noisy out here.
